data.description: FABULOUS LOCATION!! Great opportunity to own your own END UNIT TOWNHOME, next to a large cul de sac, 2b/2bath in the beautifully kept Fox Creek Crossing neighborhood!  Rentals allowed!  Open concept to dining and living area from kitchen, spacious loft and nice size bedrooms. Finished basement room that exits to patio and back yard. Great floor plan.  New water heater and HVAC system!  Terrific swim/tennis community.  Flooring is original and seller is willing to offer a flooring allowance. TRULY A MUST SEE!  Appointment required.
